elements.description:
`<vcf-autocomplete>` Web Component with a text input that provides a panel of suggested options.

```html
<vcf-autocomplete></vcf-autocomplete>
```

properties.name: _theme
properties.description:
Helper property with theme attribute value facilitating propagation
in shadow DOM.

Enables the component implementation to propagate the `theme`
attribute value to the sub-components in Shadow DOM by binding
the sub-component's "theme" attribute to the `theme` property of
the host.

**NOTE:** Extending the mixin only provides the property for binding,
and does not make the propagation alone.

See [Styling Components: Sub-components](https://vaadin.com/docs/latest/styling/custom-theme/styling-components/#sub-components).
page for more information.

properties.name: _last
properties.description: Returns true if this is the last one in the opened overlays stack

properties.name: opened
properties.description: When true, the overlay is visible and attached to body.

properties.name: owner
properties.description: Owner element passed with renderer function

properties.name: renderer
properties.description:
Custom function for rendering the content of the overlay.
Receives three arguments:

- `root` The root container DOM element. Append your content to it.
- `owner` The host element of the renderer function.
- `model` The object with the properties related with rendering.

properties.name: withBackdrop
properties.description: When true the overlay has backdrop on top of content when opened.

properties.name: model
properties.description: Object with properties that is passed to `renderer` function

properties.name: modeless
properties.description:
When true the overlay won't disable the main content, showing
it doesn't change the functionality of the user interface.

properties.name: hidden
properties.description:
When set to true, the overlay is hidden. This also closes the overlay
immediately in case there is a closing animation in progress.

properties.name: focusTrap
properties.description:
When true move focus to the first focusable element in the overlay,
or to the overlay if there are no focusable elements.

properties.name: restoreFocusOnClose
properties.description: Set to true to enable restoring of focus when overlay is closed.

properties.name: restoreFocusNode
properties.description:
Set to specify the element which should be focused on overlay close,
if `restoreFocusOnClose` is set to true.

methods.name: addController
methods.description: Registers a controller to participate in the element update cycle.

methods.name: removeController
methods.description: Removes a controller from the element.

methods.name: requestContentUpdate
methods.description:
Requests an update for the content of the overlay.
While performing the update, it invokes the renderer passed in the `renderer` property.

It is not guaranteed that the update happens immediately (synchronously) after it is requested.

methods.name: _shouldCloseOnOutsideClick
methods.description:
Whether to close the overlay on outside click or not.
Override this method to customize the closing logic.

methods.name: _outsideClickListener
methods.description:
Outside click listener used in capture phase to close the overlay before
propagating the event to the listener on the element that triggered it.
Otherwise, calling `open()` would result in closing and re-opening.

methods.name: _keydownListener
methods.description: Listener used to close whe overlay on Escape press, if it is the last one.

methods.name: bringToFront
methods.description: Brings the overlay as visually the frontmost one

events.name: vaadin-overlay-close
events.description:
vaadin-overlay-close
Fired when the opened overlay is about to be closed.
Calling `preventDefault()` on the event cancels the closing.

events.name: vaadin-overlay-closed
events.description:
vaadin-overlay-closed
Fired after the overlay is closed.

events.name: vaadin-overlay-closing
events.description:
vaadin-overlay-closing
Fired when the overlay starts to close.
Closing the overlay can be asynchronous depending on the animation.

events.name: vaadin-overlay-escape-press
events.description:
vaadin-overlay-escape-press
Fired before the overlay is closed on Escape key press.
Calling `preventDefault()` on the event cancels the closing.

events.name: vaadin-overlay-open
events.description:
vaadin-overlay-open
Fired after the overlay is opened.

events.name: vaadin-overlay-outside-click
events.description:
vaadin-overlay-outside-click

Calling `preventDefault()` on the event cancels the closing.
